OL,5,G1620 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FAt The Elan Hotel in Powys, Martin
OL,7,     Fand Iris offer a no-frills
OL,8,     Fapproach and a banging breakfast.
OL,9,     FBut the rooms lack the wow factor,
OL,10,     Fand Spencer and Gavin aren't fans
OL,11,     Fof going back to basics.
OL,12,G1650 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe final visit is to The Royal
OL,14,     FOak Inn in Somerset, run by
OL,15,     FSpencer and Gavin. After talking a
OL,16,     Fgood game all week, the guests are
OL,17,     Fshocked to find the standards to
OL,18,     Fbe rather... standard.
